  "title": "Business Support Executive (Construction/Engineering)",
  "description": "<p><em>We are seeking a </em><em><strong>Business Support Executive</strong></em><em> to provide comprehensive support to senior management, with a strong focus on </em><em><strong>budget reporting, management updates, and business operations support</strong></em><em>. This role goes beyond traditional administrative work — you will be actively involved in preparing business reports, coordinating management updates, and ensuring smooth communication across teams.</em></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare budget reports, tracking expenses, and compiling updates for management.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate executive meetings, including agendas, materials, logistics, and follow-ups.</li>\n  <li>Manage schedules, correspondence, and preparing briefing decks for senior management.</li>\n  <li>Maintain documentation and reporting systems to ensure smooth business operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or degree in Business Administration or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in <strong>business/management support</strong> in the <strong>Construction/Engineering sector.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong skills in MS Excel and PowerPoint, with hands-on experience preparing reports and presentations.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, organizational skills, and ability to work independently.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
